617
00:54:31.839 --> 00:54:32.840
El BMW.

618
00:54:47.996 --> 00:54:48.997
¡Vamos!

619
00:54:57.390 --> 00:54:58.767
Fantástico.

620
00:55:01.189 --> 00:55:04.631
